963
01:32:02,392 --> 01:32:03,100
Cinq.

964
01:32:03,685 --> 01:32:04,560
Six.

965
01:32:05,395 --> 01:32:06,270
Sept.

966
01:32:06,897 --> 01:32:07,771
Huit.

967
01:32:08,773 --> 01:32:09,315
Neuf.

968
01:32:12,444 --> 01:32:14,653
